Genital capsule
. 
Male
. Aedeagal shaft medially horizontal, tubular; apex curved anteroventrally, apex bispinose; dorsal apodeme directed dorsoposteriorly, articulating with anal tube appendage; gonopore on apogee (
Fig. 276, 277
). Plate with 4 marginal macrosetae; apex minutely serrate (
Fig. 279
). Style apophysis hook-shaped, denticulate, preapical lobe acute, anterior medial lobe relatively short, perpendicular; anterior lateral lobe elongate (
Fig. 282
).
